ISLAMABAD, May 31 (APP): Advisor to Prime Minister for Kashmir and Gilgit Baltistan Affairs Qamar Zaman Kaira on Wednesday called on Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif here.
In the meeting, they discussed the matters pertaining to the ministry as well as the overall political situation in the country, a PM Office press release said.
